text: Nancy Ellen Carell (n√©e Walls; born July 19, 1966) is an American actress, comedian and writer. She is best known for her work on Saturday Night Live, The Daily Show and The Office. In 2016, she co-created the TBS comedy series Angie Tribeca with her husband, Steve Carell.
